\\
Delays at import Customs are very common and Cases By Csera have no control over any resulting inconvenience from them. Be patient and don't panic as international shipment may take as little as one week or as much as three months on rare occasions from the shipment date which can be found of your CSERA purchase invoice. Delays are to be expected during higher-volume mailing periods, such as the pre\/post Christmas shopping, Easter season etc. Some countries customs clearance offices run extra checks at peak times, this could be due to high security alerts, threats, or additional training. \\
\\
Extreme weather conditions like hurricanes, tornadoes, floods, earthquakes and snow may effect delivery times. Public holidays and postal strikes can cause delays in packages being delivered. To check postal service public holidays, visit their website or local office to obtain information. \\
\\
FAILED DELIVERY\\
\\
Postal workers can delivery to neighbors' addresses or a family member may have accepted the delivery and not told you, the note left by the courier may have been misplaced so ensure you have checked your house\/garage\/porch\/garden and spoken to neighbors\/family before emailing us.\\
\\
Couriers will not wish to damage your CSERA package by forcing it into a full mailbox. They may leave a note stating that they tried to deliver. Some mailboxes are too small to fit CSERA packages so they will need to be left with a neighbor, taken from the courier directly or collected from their facility.\\
\\
If the courier service fails to notify you of an attempted delivery because they do not have your telephone number or the address could not be found etc, the package is stored in their facilities for 7 days and can be collected.  If it is not collected, the package will be destroyed and we cannot refund you so please check for courier notices and missed phone calls. \\

\\
CSERA cannot provide information about specific postal service systems or regulations however, if you haven't received your Cases By Csera order by the 60 calendar days we will provide proof of shipment from our postal service for you to contact your postal service for investigation.\\
\\
Any resulting inconvenience from your postal service\/customs office is to be dealt with them directly.\\
\\
\\
\\
GIFT WRAPPING AND PACKAGING\\
\\
We offer boutique gift wrapping service at no extra charge so email us at checkout if you are gift giving. All CSERA items are shipped in sturdy boxes, to prevent damage. REVIEWS\\

We are not perfect and are only human, from time to time there can be errors made on our part, but rest assured we will do everything within our power to correct our mistakes.\\
\\
Your feedback means more than you know at CSERA, please think carefully about your shopping experience at our store, take into account that your product can vary in color\/contrast\/brightness and shipping delays are not within our control. \\

Any threats, harassment, feedback extortion, impolite emails will be investigated by Etsy's Trust and Safety department, PayPal and according to country specific and international ecommerce laws. Our help is dependent upon the customer's ability to behave in a civil manner. \\

\\
\\
FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS\\

''My item did not arrive''\\
\\
Please contact Cases By Csera AFTER the 60 calendar days from the date of shipment which is on your invoice and we will be happy to help as best possible.\\

''I accidentally ordered the wrong case''\\
\\
No problem, simply send the case back to us in it's original packaging for an exchange for the correct case or a refund. Return shipping costs cannot be refunded if this was not an error in our manufacturing process\/your order. We will pay the cost of shipping the new order\/exchanged item.\\

''I didn't hear from you when I placed my order. Did you receive it?\\
\\

''If I drop my iPhone, will the case protect it? Do you guarantee my phone won't be damaged?''\\
\\
CSERA cases are economy, affordable, slim profile vanity type cases, this means they in no way protect the screen of your phone or from drop protection. If you are looking for a more protective case you may want to purchase a Otterbox style case. Please be aware of this before ordering, CSERA have sold thousands of cases to thousands of happy customers without issues. If you do need a protective drop type case we often suggest a commercial product like the Otterbox and not a designer\/vanity case such as ours.\\
\\
''What is a 'vanity case?'\\
\\
Vanity cases are designed for fashion purposes and offer light protection for mobile devices. The price you pay is for the professionally designed artwork, the time it takes for me to make the case and packaging. CSERA cases are all limited edition and cannot be purchased elsewhere, meaning the artwork is completely unique and copyright protected.\\
